item.title: asakura
item.description: Asakura is real estate brand from Japan that specializes in the sale of apartments, including new and luxury ones. Asakura has been a part of the Japanese market since the 1960s, and they have a good reputation for their service and their apartments. Asakura offers a wide range of properties, from townhouses to luxury apartments, so there is something for everyone. They also specialize in luxury apartments in Tokyo, so if you are looking for something more than just a starter apartment, you will find what you need here.

borgogna art gallery
item.description: The Borgogne Art Gallery was founded in 1970 by Angelo Scanzia. Borgagna Art Gallery is located in Borgogna, a small town in northern Italy. Its collection includes paintings, sculptures, and decorative objects. The gallery has a large collection of contemporary art, like abstract art, photography, mixed media and many more. Borgogna Art is an art gallery, a place where you can see and buy contemporary art in large collections. Art gallery brands are not only for artists to sell their art.
